AllPrintings.description: Files containing all cards, including all printings and variations, categorized by set.

AllPrintingsCSVFiles.description: Files containing a directory of .csv files containing all data from AllPrintings.json.

AllDeckFiles.description: Files containing all pre-constructed decks, compressed.

AllIdentifiers.description: Files containing all cards organized by UUID.

AllPrices.description: Files containing all prices of cards in various formats.

AllSetFiles.description: Files containing each individual set file in a directory, compressed.

AtomicCards.description: Files containing every card as a unique "atomic" object.

CardTypes.description: Files containing every card type of any type of card.

CompiledList.description: Files containing all possible compiled outputs from MTGJSON, such as AllPrintings, CardTypes, etc.

DeckList.description: Files containing all possible compiled pre-constructed deck outputs from MTGJSON.

EnumValues.description: Files containing known property values for data models. Used primarily for internal documentation but still available to the public.

Keywords.description: Files containing a list of all keywords used on Magic cards.

Legacy.description: Files containing all sets, restricted to sets legal in the Legacy format.

LegacyAtomic.description: Files containing all cards, restricted to cards legal in the Legacy format.

Meta.description: Files containing the metadata object, has {{link@ISO 8601@https://www.iso.org/iso-8601-date-and-time-format.html}} dates for latest build and prices, and version properties of this MTGJSON release.

PauperAtomic.description: Files containing all cards, restricted to cards legal in the Pauper format.

Pioneer.description: Files containing all sets, restricted to sets legal in the Pioneer format.

PioneerAtomic.description: Files containing all cards, restricted to cards legal in the Pioneer format.

Modern.description: Files containing all sets, restricted to sets legal in the Modern format.

ModernAtomic.description: Files containing all cards, restricted to cards legal in the Modern format.

SetList.description: Files containing a list of codes, names and release dates of all sets.

Standard.description: Files containing all sets, restricted to sets legal in the Standard format.

StandardAtomic.description: Files containing all cards, restricted to cards legal in the Standard format.

Vintage.description: Files containing all sets, restricted to sets legal in the Vintage format.

VintageAtomic.description: Files containing all cards, restricted to cards legal in the Vintage format.
